WEBVTT

1
00:00:13.340 --> 00:00:13.820
Kia ora!

2
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:16.900
I tēnei akoranga, ka tirohia e tātou

3
00:00:16.900 --> 00:00:18.500
ngā āhuatanga o ia whārangi i roto i te

4
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:20.600
taupānga TreeSpotter me te whakamahi i aua āhuatanga.

5
00:00:21.540 --> 00:00:22.940
Ka tīmata ki te whārangi mahere.

6
00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:31.060
He whakamahara, he whakaaturanga tauira tēnei ataata,

7
00:00:31.060 --> 00:00:33.220
ā, tērā pea ka rerekē te paetukutuku whakamutunga i tēnei ataata.

8
00:00:34.080 --> 00:00:36.340
Hei tīmata i te rapu, pāwhiritia te pae rapu

9
00:00:36.340 --> 00:00:38.340
kei te tahua mauī, kātahi ka pēhi i te Enter

10
00:00:38.340 --> 00:00:38.780
ina oti koe.

11
00:00:39.700 --> 00:00:41.300
Me rapu tātou i tētahi rākau āporo.

12
00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:51.980
Ina utaina mai ngā hua rapu,

13
00:00:51.980 --> 00:00:53.640
kōwhiria tētahi rākau mā te pāwhiri

14
00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:55.880
i tōna ingoa i te rārangi hua rapu,

15
00:00:55.880 --> 00:00:57.520
rānei, ka taea hoki e koe te pāwhiri

16
00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:57.520
i tōna wāhi kua tohua ki te mahere.

17
00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:38.860
Hei tīmata i te whakatere, pāwhiritia te pātene

18
00:01:38.860 --> 00:01:40.300
"Navigate" kei raro i ngā taipitopito o te rākau.

19
00:01:43.580 --> 00:01:45.880
I konei, ka taea e koe te kōwhiri i tō momo haere

20
00:01:45.880 --> 00:01:47.700
mai i te tahua, ka pāwhiri rānei i te "Start"

21
00:01:47.700 --> 00:01:49.780
hei tīmata i te whakatere, ā, ka tukuna koe ki tētahi

22
00:01:49.780 --> 00:01:50.980
matapihi OpenStreetMap.